{"tid":2042910,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[反國安法]\"反詩\"兩首","createTime":"2020-05-30T05:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:13:50.000Z","uid":262389,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0c01caa806b7e9e34df514f2393eb1fb93b37823","tid":2042910,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"以下兩首詩，好可能係國安法實施之後被定性為&quot;反詩&quot;，希望大家可以做個見證，到時仲可以見到我。<br />\n<br />\n《十年未晚》<br />\n<br />\n光輝不再待從頭<br />\n復興無期空悲切<br />\n香火欲斷留殘志<br />\n港灣遠去別傷城<br />\n<br />\n時光飛逝殘燭去<br />\n代有英雄豪傑出<br />\n革新還待青松至<br />\n命定終須少年來<br />\n<br />\n《作今明－香港》<br />\n<br />\n昨日繁花盛，百家互爭鳴<br />\n墟市接天際，商旅滿舟船<br />\n毋須朝夕令，仍見治安寧<br />\n終歸易轅轍，頃刻成絕景<br />\n<br />\n今日無所剩，百花盡凋零<br />\n良人絕於野，鄉舍不復存<br />\n欲違中樞命，再見是清明<br />\n當即立宏志，不屈義填膺<br />\n<br />\n明日誰可定，捨身開太平<br />\n民志不可奪，薪火永相傳<br />\n重光還清政，復見盡光榮<br />\n必將換旗幟，衷心成願景"},{"pid":"7898c3d531eccbe952d9895717c0c650c0745315","tid":2042910,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26675747f16ba459494c74b4565756f51311c9e3","tid":2042910,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"但願"},{"pid":"c33a2e072ec8193189f889112f40d3f4a2ada7ca","tid":2042910,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n9/10 !!!!"},{"pid":"f6b81e85cc059dae82970e51e10943c4aa53bcff","tid":2042910,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"oh my god"},{"pid":"8e86ffef5a629a1a72189f299a13838754dc2de2","tid":2042910,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"